To all the trolls leaving negative comments here under the guise of "constructive criticism", you're truely just cruel, petty and immature people, and I hope you do some growing up this year.

I love Ten (for example) and bought his album too, though just happen to be more into Taeyong's style. But why would I go to Ten's video to leave "constructive critisism" even if I didn't like his songs? - I'm pretty sure Ten doesn't need my help in that area.
